review.reviewBody: Was recommended by a friend, honestly was sceptical at first, but it's to die for!!! will keep coming back for sure!  I had  The Big Yum Bow bowl and the mushroom calamari, they are to die for the Oyster Myshroom Calamari gives cactus club truffle fries a run for their money  !! Highly recommend this even for those who aren't sure or for those looking for a healthy option, trust me get those two items and you will see !!!
Nashvi Hunny Glazed Mac n Cheez Donuts ◊‡lle is my new favourite comfort food. So good!
Tastes amazing burgers are great and so are the fries when they remember to include them
Awesome & very tasty portions for Bowls & Fries!! Especially favorite the big yum bowl.  Never forgets my mayo dips. Just would love fryer cleaned more, better cooked fries.

The poutine is so good! It always arrives too cold despite living 17 mins away but the way they package it makes it easy to reheat. 
4 stars this time because the portion was smaller than usual.
